### 3. Create `.gitignore`

Create a file named `.gitignore` and add this:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
ENV/
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Logs
stove_calculations_log.csv

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/